thread.title_full: Frames Direct reviewed by S. Brown

author: S. Brown
title: S. Brown
text: At first I was hesitant because of mixed reviews online for frames direct. My transaction was great. I placed the order and after a few days for processing (as stated on the website) my glasses were shipped and delivered. Super fast shipping and an awesome quality product at a lower price than most other sites.
